size and position of a window under the cursor, even if\
it's not frontmost.\
1.\
2.\
Place your cursor over a window\
Hold the configured modifiers or mouse button, or\
execute a configured trackapad gesture\
3. Move your cursor to select a size/position\
4. Release the modifiers, mouse button, or touch from\
trackpad to snap the window into place
